name: Khin Myat Noe Zaw
bio: My passion for architecture is fueled by a fascination with spaces that promote healing and interaction. As a student about to embark on my master's journey, I am eager to explore the power of thoughtful design that enhances well-being and foster connections within communities. Through my studies, I aim to develop innovative solutions that create more inclusive, supportive, and harmonious environments for people to thrive in.
